frameworks:
- electron
- some css framework
    - something with a good looking table
- some js component framework
    - probably vue
    - maybe react if we can find a good table component
- webpack
- modern js; no pre-es6 bs
    - dont care about ie compatibility
    
goals:
- keyboard shortcuts for quick editing, adding, and deleting rows and cells
- array columns (mult items per cell)
- links 
    - object literal: {title, link} 
    - markdown string: "[title](link)"
    - ctrl-k shortcut (defaults to object literal)
- open/save in json, yml, csv, and md
- fast loading times
- sidebar file browser
- properties file per-folder
    - per table:
        - color
        - dropdown columns

https://denisraslov.github.io/grid/
- things this is missing:
    - delete cells and rows using keyboard
    - re-order rows using keyboard
    - search by tags
- things this has:
    - lazy loading
    - can handle thousands of rows
    - api for editing cells
    
    
